00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:40,900
Poďte sem!

355
00:22:40,910 --> 00:22:42,190
Tae Gong Sil?

356
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:52,300
Čo robíš s tou bábikou?

357
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:56,320
Ty...

358
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:59,000
si sa teraz rozprávala s bábikou?

359
00:23:00,370 --> 00:23:01,610
Viem všetko.

360
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:03,280
Pretože som to videl niekoľkokrát.

361
00:23:03,290 --> 00:23:04,580
Videl si všetko?

362
